This one is a HUGE hit! Our dinner guests all laughed at the chickens over the beer cans -- they stopped laughing as soon as they tried it. I replaced the cayenne with finely ground dried chipotle, and tripled the rub recipe to do two 3 - 3 1/2 lb. chickens (gotta be generous with the rub, it's a must).

Rating: 3
A fun recipe to prepare. The chicken sitting on the beer can is a wonderfully comical sight. I cooked the chicken on my Weber gas grill for 1 1/2 hours at med./low. I would be more generous with the rub the next time around.

